# 4.3.3 2012/01/03 - Add check for 2pT13 for various abilities.
# 4.3.2 2011/12/29 - Update Arms rotation to r10711 and Fury Rotation to r10727.
#                    Check for Tactical Mastery before stance-dancing in Arms rotation.
# 4.3.1 2011/12/15 - Initial version based on Ovale default script.
#                    Use warrior profiles from SimulationCraft, Tier 13H:
#                        Arms (r10571), Fury-1H (r10571), Fury-2H (r10571)

